{"data":[{"date":"11:02 09/08","title":"Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Roma treo th\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1eb1ng si\u00eau xe Lamborghini","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/chu-tich-roma-treo-thuong-bang-sieu-xe-lamborghini.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"5283","checkdouble":"194092"},{"date":"11:10 09/08","title":"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Firmino tr\u1ea3 vi\u1ec7n ph\u00ed c\u1ee9u s\u1ed1ng 2 tr\u1ebb em Brazil","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/9/tien-dao-firmino-tra-vien-phi-cuu-song-2-tre-em-brazil.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Roberto Firmino \u0111\u00e3 chi tr\u1ea3 1 n\u0103m vi\u1ec7n ph\u00ed c\u1ee9u s\u1ed1ng 2 tr\u1ebb em m\u1eafc b\u1ec7nh hi\u1ec3m ngh\u00e8o \u1edf qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 Brazil.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">The Sun \u0111\u01b0a tin Roberto Firmino v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 60.000 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee9u s\u1ed1ng hai \u0111\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil m\u1eafc b\u1ec7nh hi\u1ec3m ngh\u00e8o. Joao de Amorim (6 tu\u1ed5i) v\u00e0 Miguel de Amorim (11 th\u00e1ng tu\u1ed5i) b\u1ecb ch\u1ea9n \u0111o\u00e1n m\u1eafc ch\u1ee9ng teo c\u01a1 c\u1ed9t s\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfm g\u1eb7p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCha m\u1eb9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tr\u1ea3 chi ph\u00ed \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb t\u1ed1n k\u00e9m l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 827.000 b\u1ea3ng. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 k\u00eau g\u1ecdi tr\u00ean ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng v\u1edbi hy v\u1ecdng quy\u00ean g\u00f3p \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1eefa tr\u1ecb cho 2 \u0111\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Firmino tr\u1ea3 vi\u1ec7n ph\u00ed c\u1ee9u s\u1ed1ng 2 tr\u1ebb em Brazil h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Firmino tr\u1ea3 vi\u1ec7n ph\u00ed c\u1ee9u s\u1ed1ng 2 tr\u1ebb em Brazil h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/1_1.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Roberto Firmino v\u00e0 v\u1ee3.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn tai Roberto Firmino, v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n cho gia \u0111\u00ecnh nh\u00e0 Amorim s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 60.000 b\u1ea3ng. Kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 gia \u0111\u00ecnh Amorim trang tr\u1ea3i trong 1 n\u0103m \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1edd th\u00eam c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 h\u1ea3o t\u00e2m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00e0 Schlemmer, m\u1eb9 c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng: \"Larissa Pereira, v\u1ee3 c\u1ee7a Firmino \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean l\u1ea1c v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u00e0 n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng c\u00f4 \u1ea5y s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. T\u00f4i kh\u00f3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, b\u1edfi kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi hai \u0111\u1ee9a con c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong \u0111o\u1ea1n clip c\u1ea3m \u01a1n tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i, c\u1ea3 gia \u0111\u00ecnh nh\u00e0 Amorim \u0111\u1ec1u m\u1eb7c chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u Liverpool v\u00e0 d\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 bi\u1ebft \u01a1n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t cho v\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng Roberto Firmino.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\"Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0m cha m\u1eb9 v\u00e0 hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1ed7i \u0111au gia \u0111\u00ecnh h\u1ecd \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu. Roberto \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i\", Larissa Pereira - b\u00e0 x\u00e3 c\u1ee7a Firmino chia s\u1ebb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nR\u1ed1i lo\u1ea1n th\u1ea7n kinh c\u01a1 (SMA) l\u00e0 ch\u1ee9ng b\u1ec7nh di truy\u1ec1n hi\u1ebfm g\u1eb7p do m\u1ea5t \u0111i c\u00e1c noron v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 t\u00e0n ph\u00e1 c\u01a1, g\u00e2y t\u1eed vong s\u1edbm \u1edf tr\u1ebb em.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5282","checkdouble":"194095"},{"date":"09:33 09/08","title":"\"Ronaldo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a Juve \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ea7m cao m\u1edbi\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/30/ronaldo-co-the-dua-juve-den-tam-cao-moi.jpeg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Bom t\u1ea5n c\u1ee7a Juventus m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn t\u1eeb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Douglas Costa ca ng\u1ee3i Ronaldo s\u1ebd n\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nCosta \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o CR7<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau 9 n\u0103m kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real Madrid v\u00e0 ghi t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 450 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ra \u0111i t\u00ecm th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi. Anh \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n sang Juventus v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 115 tri\u1ec7u euro m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, v\u00e0 \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd t\u1eeb gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean, nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Bianconeri c\u0169ng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1edbi. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady, h\u1ecd c\u00f2n tin t\u01b0\u1edfng CR7 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League, \u0111i\u1ec1u Juventus kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 si\u00eau sao m\u1edbi gia nh\u1eadp CLB, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Douglas Costa cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Ronaldo \u1edf m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t, anh \u1ea5y \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfn th\u00eam m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc n\u1eefa trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 CR7 c\u00f3 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ea7m cao m\u1edbi, anh \u1ea5y s\u1ebd l\u00e0m n\u00ean nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Douglas Costa ca ng\u1ee3i Ronaldo s\u1ebd n\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m Juventus\" title=\"Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus b\u00e1o hi\u1ec7u s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed5i thay c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 Serie A.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/ronaldo-11.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Douglas Costa ca ng\u1ee3i Ronaldo s\u1ebd n\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m Juventus</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Ronaldo l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, h\u01a1n n\u1eefa ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f2n c\u00f3 Paulo Dybala v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng Neymar, b\u1edfi v\u1eady s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng khi Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng, anh \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n n\u1eefa, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 che gi\u1ea5u.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y, khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u00fd k\u1ebft, Juventus s\u1ebd coi h\u1ecd nh\u01b0 gia \u0111\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Juventus l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Allegri l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t HLV tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u00f3 kh\u00e1t khao l\u1edbn v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y gi\u00fap ch\u00fang t\u00f4i tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n h\u01a1n.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Douglas Costa ca ng\u1ee3i Ronaldo, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng Serie A m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111ang ch\u1edd xem li\u1ec7u CR7 c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh gi\u00e0nh C1 hay kh\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/co-cristiano-ronaldo-serie-a-doi-logo-176-194058.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/co-cristiano-ronaldo-serie-a-doi-logo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/co-cristiano-ronaldo-serie-a-doi-logo-176-194058.html\">C\u00f3 Cristiano Ronaldo, Serie A CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C \u0111\u1ed5i sang logo m\u1edbi</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c s\u1edf h\u1eefu si\u00eau sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi l\u00e0 Cristiano Ronaldo, Serie A m\u00f9a n\u00e0y t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1edbn v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n khi chia tay logo c\u0169 sang th\u00e0nh m\u1eabu...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/ronaldo-va-bo-nhanh-chong-hoa-nhap-vao-xu-mi-ong-188-193946.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/ronaldo-va-bo-nhanh-chong-hoa-nhap-vao-xu-mi-ong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/hau-truong/ronaldo-va-bo-nhanh-chong-hoa-nhap-vao-xu-mi-ong-188-193946.html\">Ronaldo v\u00e0 b\u1ed3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u00e0o x\u1ee9 m\u00ec \u1ed1ng</span><br>\r\nT\u00e2n binh Cristiano Ronaldo c\u1ee7a Juventus \u0111ang nh\u1eadp gia t\u00f9y t\u1ee5c c\u1ef1c nhanh v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng m\u1edbi t\u1ea1i Italia. S\u1ef1 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp \u00eam nh\u01b0 ru c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u00f3...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5281","checkdouble":"194082"},{"date":"09:11 09/08","title":"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam: \u201cC\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u00ec do k\u00e9m chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/olympic-viet-nam-cac-cau-thu-bi-loai-khong-phai-vi-do-kem-chuyen-mon.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u00fd gi\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, c\u1ea3 c\u1ef1u HLV \u0110o\u00e0n Minh X\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n D\u01b0\u01a1ng V\u0169 L\u00e2m \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 k\u00e9m.</h2><h2>&ldquo;C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 k\u00e9m&quot;</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c 20 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 trong tay HLV Park Hang Seo l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 k\u00e9m c\u1ecfi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0n v\u1ec1 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m h\u01a1n 2 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n kh\u00e1c c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018, g\u1ed3m Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Ho\u00e0ng v\u00e0 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng: hay Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng, Ti\u1ebfn Linh \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u1ea1i V-League 2018.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u00ec do k\u00e9m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u00ec do k\u00e9m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/cc2-3596-1533696911.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam&nbsp;\u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u00ec k\u00e9m chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 l\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u00fd do \u00f4ng \u01b0u ti\u00ean ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, c\u1ef1u HLV \u0110o\u00e0n Minh X\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn: &ldquo;M\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd danh s\u00e1ch 20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 Asiad, so v\u1edbi 23 ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1c. N\u00ean HLV s\u1ebd ch\u1ecdn nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t c\u00e0ng \u0111a n\u0103ng c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t, \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9 v\u1edbi ch\u1eebng \u0111\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng Park v\u1eabn s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1c nhau&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, Quang H\u1ea3i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1eeba \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c v\u1eeba \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh. \u0110\u1ee9c Huy v\u1eeba \u0111\u00e1 c\u00e1nh, v\u1eeba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, V\u0103n H\u1eadu v\u1eeba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 bi\u00ean, v\u1eeba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 trung v\u1ec7. Hay V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft, V\u0103n To\u00e0n, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1eeba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec3n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, v\u1eeba c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o l\u00f9i. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n gi\u1eefa h\u1ecd so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc nh\u01b0 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng, Ti\u1ebfn Linh, T\u1ea5n Sinh hay Tri\u1ec7u Vi\u1ec7t H\u01b0ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed3ng quan \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00ean, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 Asiad, \u00f4ng D\u01b0\u01a1ng V\u0169 L\u00e2m c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u00ec h\u1ecd d\u1edf h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn, m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi ASIAD, HLV Park Hang Seo c\u1ea7n c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng nhi\u1ec1u ti\u00eau ch\u00ed.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Indonesia trong \u00edt ng\u00e0y n\u1eefa. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean g\u1eb7p Olympic Pakistan v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 14, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Oman v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0o c\u00e1c ng\u00e0y 16 v\u00e0 19/8.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/dt-olympic-thai-lan-dat-muc-tieu-khong-tuong-tai-asiad-292-194075.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/dt-olympic-thai-lan-dat-muc-tieu-khong-tuong-tai-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/dt-olympic-thai-lan-dat-muc-tieu-khong-tuong-tai-asiad-292-194075.html\">\u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1ea1i ASIAD</span><br />\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y song G\u0110 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt Witthaya Laohakul v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c \u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan s\u1ebd v\u00e0o t\u1edbi...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-hagl-noi-gi-khi-bi-loai-khoi-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-168-194060.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/sao-hagl-noi-gi-khi-bi-loai-khoi-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-hagl-noi-gi-khi-bi-loai-khoi-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-168-194060.html\">Sao HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD?</span><br />\r\nL\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 10 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u1ea7n Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i song anh c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u sau...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/loai-van-lam-hlv-park-hang-seo-da-noi-gi-voi-thu-mon-nay-168-194057.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/loai-van-lam-hlv-park-hang-seo-da-noi-gi-voi-thu-mon-nay.JPG\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/loai-van-lam-hlv-park-hang-seo-da-noi-gi-voi-thu-mon-nay-168-194057.html\">Lo\u1ea1i V\u0103n L\u00e2m, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y?</span><br />\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 ri\u00eang v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m. V\u00e0 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5280","checkdouble":"194083"},{"date":"09:38 09/08","title":"HLV H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/hlv-han-quoc-noi-gi-sau-khi-u23-viet-nam-vo-dich-giai-giao-huu.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn h\u1ecd l\u00ean ng\u00f4i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</h2><h2>HLV H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo</h2>\r\nV\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c v\u00e0 \u00edt \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ed9 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 23 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch r\u1ea5t x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng.<br />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a HLV \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u1edf ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch giao h\u1eefu h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch giao h\u1eefu h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/IMG_1418.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao&nbsp;\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam khi v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do v\u1ecb n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed 2 &ldquo;gi\u00e1n \u0111i\u1ec7p&rdquo; t\u1eeb H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c sang theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 ghi ch\u00e9p v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Vinaphone Cup 2018. V\u00e0 sau khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng b\u00e1o c\u00e1o ghi ch\u00e9p c\u1ee7a hai v\u1ecb n\u00e0y, HLV Kim Hak-bum c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi n\u00e0y n\u00f3i v\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c: &quot;M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Son Heung-min \u1edf c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng knock-out v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh, v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t hay nh\u01b0 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan, l\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t \u1edf khu v\u1ef1c \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u1edf \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, v\u00ec ngo\u00e0i chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n th\u00ec y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft c\u0169ng gi\u00fap c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00e0y ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quen v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u1ea9m v\u00e0 n\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y. C\u0169ng nh\u01b0 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u1edf Indonesia&quot;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m t\u1ea1i ASIAD, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng E c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Kyrgyzstan, Malaysia v\u00e0 Bahrain. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Kim chi gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng n\u00e0y c\u00f2n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ee9ng nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng D th\u00ec hai \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p nhau \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fd do ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n \u0111\u00e3 theo r\u1ea5t s\u00e1t th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch kh\u1eafc ch\u1ebf \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-cac-cau-thu-bi-loai-khong-phai-vi-do-kem-chuyen-mon-168-194083.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/olympic-viet-nam-cac-cau-thu-bi-loai-khong-phai-vi-do-kem-chuyen-mon.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-cac-cau-thu-bi-loai-khong-phai-vi-do-kem-chuyen-mon-168-194083.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam: &ldquo;C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u00ec do k\u00e9m chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n&rdquo;</span><br />\r\nL\u00fd gi\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, c\u1ea3 c\u1ef1u HLV \u0110o\u00e0n Minh X\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n D\u01b0\u01a1ng V\u0169 L\u00e2m \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/dt-olympic-thai-lan-dat-muc-tieu-khong-tuong-tai-asiad-292-194075.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/dt-olympic-thai-lan-dat-muc-tieu-khong-tuong-tai-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/dt-olympic-thai-lan-dat-muc-tieu-khong-tuong-tai-asiad-292-194075.html\">\u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1ea1i ASIAD</span><br />\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y song G\u0110 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt Witthaya Laohakul v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c \u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan s\u1ebd v\u00e0o t\u1edbi...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-hagl-noi-gi-khi-bi-loai-khoi-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-168-194060.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/sao-hagl-noi-gi-khi-bi-loai-khoi-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-hagl-noi-gi-khi-bi-loai-khoi-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-168-194060.html\">Sao HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD?</span><br />\r\nL\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 10 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u1ea7n Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i song anh c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u sau...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;&#10;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5279","checkdouble":"194086"},{"date":"11:04 09/08","title":"C\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf ASIAD","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/7/cuu-thuyen-truong-thai-lan-danh-gia-ve-co-hoi-cua-olympic-viet-nam-o-asiad.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu Vinaphone Cup, c\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Th\u00e1i Lan, \u00f4ng Steve Darby \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf ASIAD.</h2><h2>HLV Steve Darby n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Steve Darby n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Steve Darby n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/HLV-Steve-Darby-noi-gi-ve-co-hoi-cua-Olympic-Viet-Nam-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u1ef1u HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Th\u00e1i Lan d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn xa \u1edf ASIAD</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo k\u1ebft th\u00fac gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu Vinaphone Cup 2018 v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi th\u1eafng 2 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 h\u00f2a 1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 b\u1edfi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 y\u1ebfu b\u1edfi h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111ang trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, v\u1ecb c\u1ef1u HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Th\u00e1i Lan, \u00f4ng Steve Darby \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen: \"C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e0 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. D\u00f9 r\u1eb1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 m\u1edbi quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 qu\u1ea3 quy\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec sau 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng, song t\u00f4i tin \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 s\u1ebd l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out c\u1ee7a ASIAD\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u01a1i co c\u1ee5m ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 t\u1ea1i Th\u01b0\u1eddng Ch\u00e2u h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 1,\u00a0c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 kh\u00e1c khi d\u00e1m ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00f4i c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch k\u1ebft li\u1ec5u \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, \u00f4ng Steve Darby v\u1eabn hy v\u1ecdng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd gi\u1eef v\u1eefng tinh th\u1ea7n v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 t\u1ec9nh t\u00e1o \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i ASIAD.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y ch\u1ed1t l\u1ea1i: \"H\u00e3y gi\u1eef c\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea7u l\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh, qu\u1ea3 ng\u1ecdt s\u1ebd t\u1edbi v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Khi gi\u1eef v\u1eefng tinh th\u1ea7n trong m\u1ecdi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng, c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n lo l\u1eafng g\u00ec c\u1ea3\".<br />\r\n\u00a0</p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/7/Highlight-U23-Viet-Nam-vs-U23-Uzbekistan.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-han-quoc-noi-gi-sau-khi-u23-viet-nam-vo-dich-giai-giao-huu-168-194086.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/hlv-han-quoc-noi-gi-sau-khi-u23-viet-nam-vo-dich-giai-giao-huu.JPG\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-han-quoc-noi-gi-sau-khi-u23-viet-nam-vo-dich-giai-giao-huu-168-194086.html\">HLV H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu</span><br />\r\nNh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn h\u1ecd l\u00ean ng\u00f4i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-cac-cau-thu-bi-loai-khong-phai-vi-do-kem-chuyen-mon-168-194083.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/olympic-viet-nam-cac-cau-thu-bi-loai-khong-phai-vi-do-kem-chuyen-mon.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-cac-cau-thu-bi-loai-khong-phai-vi-do-kem-chuyen-mon-168-194083.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam: \u201cC\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u00ec do k\u00e9m chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n\u201d</span><br />\r\nL\u00fd gi\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, c\u1ea3 c\u1ef1u HLV \u0110o\u00e0n Minh X\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n D\u01b0\u01a1ng V\u0169 L\u00e2m \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/dt-olympic-thai-lan-dat-muc-tieu-khong-tuong-tai-asiad-292-194075.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/dt-olympic-thai-lan-dat-muc-tieu-khong-tuong-tai-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/dt-olympic-thai-lan-dat-muc-tieu-khong-tuong-tai-asiad-292-194075.html\">\u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1ea1i ASIAD</span><br />\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y song G\u0110 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt Witthaya Laohakul v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c \u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan s\u1ebd v\u00e0o t\u1edbi...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:\n115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5278","checkdouble":"194093"},{"date":"10:45 09/08","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! Top 10 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/9/day-top-10-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 bom t\u1ea5n 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Kepa c\u1ee7a Chelsea v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Alisson \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u Top 10 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\n10 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 &ldquo;ch\u01a1i l\u1edbn&rdquo; khi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u00edch n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n Kepa Arrizabalaga v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u euro (71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng). S\u1edf d\u0129 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 l\u1ea1i cao \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eady, b\u1edfi h\u1ecd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec3 qua m\u1eb7t Atletic Bilbao, gi\u00fap th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 23 tu\u1ed5i tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Alisson Becker c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng ngao ng\u00e1n v\u00ec qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft (67 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng &ndash; g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ebfp sau l\u00e0 Ederson). Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh s\u1ed1 2 \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u1ee7a The Blues, HLV Jurgen Klopp \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tr\u00fat b\u1ecf g\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Top 10 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi: Kepa v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Alisson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/kep.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Top 10 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi: Kepa v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Alisson</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, Thibaut Courtois c\u0169ng l\u1ecdt Top 10 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1, khi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Real Madrid v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 31 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng (35 tri\u1ec7u euro). S\u1edf d\u0129 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t r\u1ebb nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, b\u1edfi anh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 1 n\u0103m v\u1edbi CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n, v\u00e0 c\u0169ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i ra s\u00e2n t\u1eadp.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Top 10 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb 6 qu\u1ed1c gia, v\u1edbi Italia, T\u00e2y Ban Nha, \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 Brazil s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed7i qu\u1ed1c gia 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi. C\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 Anh (Jordan Pickford) v\u00e0 B\u1ec9 (Thibaut Coutois).<br>\r\n<strong><br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div><strong>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u