ext .5pt;mso-border-left-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;&#10;  mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt;height:15.85pt\">\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;&#10;  text-align:center;line-height:normal;mso-element:frame;mso-element-frame-hspace:&#10;  9.0pt;mso-element-wrap:around;mso-element-anchor-vertical:paragraph;&#10;  mso-element-anchor-horizontal:margin;mso-element-left:center;mso-element-top:&#10;  -.75pt;mso-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">71</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/voi-alisson-premier-league-chiem-tron-hang-thu-dat-gia-nhat-hanh-tinh-172-191635.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/26/voi-alisson-premier-league-chiem-tron-hang-thu-dat-gia-nhat-hanh-tinh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/voi-alisson-premier-league-chiem-tron-hang-thu-dat-gia-nhat-hanh-tinh-172-191635.html\">V\u1edbi Alisson, Premier League chi\u1ebfm tr\u1ecdn h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson Becker v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb h\u01a1n...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-chelsea-don-kepa-voi-gia-ky-luc-172-194065.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/chuyen-nhuong-premier-league-ngay-dong-cua.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-chelsea-don-kepa-voi-gia-ky-luc-172-194065.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Chelsea k\u00edch n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kepa Arrizabalaga \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c l\u00e0 71.8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nNguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5277","checkdouble":"194091"},{"date":"11:32 09/08","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 09/08","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/6/chuyen-nhuong-real-madrid-hot-nhat-ngay-0908.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a Los Blancos \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 09/08.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Navas tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 0908 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 0908 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/Chuyen-nhuong-Real-Madrid-2018-hot-nhat-ngay-0908-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&nbsp;Keylor Navas kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKeylor Navas ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Real Madrid. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 31 tu\u1ed5i th\u00e0 ch\u1ebft ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu khu\u1ea5t ph\u1ee5c trong cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi t\u00e2n binh Thibaut&nbsp;Courtois.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/keylor-navas-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-tai-real-madrid-180-194072.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/Chuyen-nhuong-Real-Madrid-2018-hot-nhat-ngay-0908-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/keylor-navas-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-tai-real-madrid-180-194072.html\">Sao b\u1ecb th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng c\u1ee7a Real th\u1ec1 ch\u1ebft &ldquo;chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u&rdquo; c\u00f9ng Courtois</span><br>\r\nKeylor Navas ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Real Madrid. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 31 tu\u1ed5i th\u00e0 ch\u1ebft ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu khu\u1ea5t ph\u1ee5c trong cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi t\u00e2n binh Thibaut Courtois.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Kovacic</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00eda Chelsea ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c b\u00e1n th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Courtois cho Real Madrid v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kovacic ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn Stamford Bridge nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng cho Chelsea theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m kh\u00f4ng k\u00e8m \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Courtois ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid v\u1eeba ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 vi\u1ec7c mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Thibaut Courtois t\u1eeb Chelsea v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Los Blancos theo b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 6 n\u0103m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Real Madrid ch\u1ed1t 70 tri\u1ec7u euro cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Modric</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsa muon mua Pjanic\" title=\"Chelsa mu\u1ed1n mua Pjanic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/real-madrid-chot-70-trieu-euro-cho-nguoi-thay-the-modric.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real mu\u1ed1n mua Pjanic thay Modric</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Miralem Pjanic thay Luka Modric, Los Blancos ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 70 tri\u1ec7u euro mua ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Juventus.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Real Madrid s\u1eafp bi\u1ebfn Harry Kane \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Harry Kane c\u1ee7a Tottenham \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 250 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Spurs nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-sap-bien-harry-kane-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-180-193833.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/28/real-madrid-sap-bien-harry-kane-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-sap-bien-harry-kane-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-180-193833.html\">Real Madrid s\u1eafp bi\u1ebfn Harry Kane \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</span><br>\r\nReal Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Harry Kane c\u1ee7a Tottenham \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 250 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Spurs nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Salah cho Real</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Don Balon, chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real 2018 d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi 200 tri\u1ec7u euro mua ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Salah c\u1ee7a Liverpool, song ph\u00eda The Kop tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i cho Los Blancos.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Lucas Vazquez mu\u1ed1n Real gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0y?</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luka Modric\" title=\"Luka Modric\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/Luka-Modric.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Vazquez mu\u1ed1n Real gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Luka Modric</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lucas Vazquez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Luka Modric, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha hy v\u1ecdng Real Madrid s\u1ebd gi\u1eef b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Real ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua sao Arsenal</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Marca, Real Madrid c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ramsey c\u1ee7a Arsenal. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 1 n\u0103m nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5276","checkdouble":"194097"},{"date":"10:10 09/08","title":"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 Top 4 Premier League","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/huyen-thoai-du-doan-bat-ngo-ve-top-4-premier-league.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o l\u1eebng danh c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Top 4 Premier League 2018/19 \u2013 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1ebd kh\u1edfi tranh v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 S\u00e1u n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nShearer d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n 4 CLB d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Alan Shearer m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City s\u1ebd b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Liverpool d\u00f9 chi ti\u00eau r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh tay, nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch \u1edf ng\u00f4i \u00c1 qu\u00e2n. 2 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Shearer cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;M\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 chi ti\u1ec1n t\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec3 thu h\u1eb9p kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n ch\u00fang. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecf ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi \u00e1p l\u1ef1c th\u00e0nh t\u00edch n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1. Jurgen Klopp hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng th\u00e0 ch\u1ecbu s\u1ee9c \u00e9p khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi ti\u00eau, c\u00f2n h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ee9ng y\u00ean so v\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i n\u00e0o.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alan Shearer nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Top 4 Premier League 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Alan Shearer nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Top 4 Premier League 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/Alan-Shearer-nhan-dinh-Top-4-Premier-League-201819-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Alan Shearer&nbsp;nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Top 4 Premier League 2018/19: Liverpool th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Tottenham kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o cho \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ngu\u1ed3n t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh d\u1ed3i d\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean kh\u00e1c, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Mourinho d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng m\u1ea5t vi\u1ec7c, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ch\u00fang ta nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y tr\u00ean truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh. Ai bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c M.U s\u1ebd th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t n\u00e0o tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf? V\u1edbi t\u00f4i, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 v\u00e0 s\u1ebd th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c ngai v\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a Man City m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Nh\u1eefng CLB n\u1eb1m ngo\u00e0i Top 4, theo t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0 Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal. C\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng HLV m\u1edbi v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u01a1n, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n. Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Man City v\u1eabn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 CLB gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u00ec h\u1ecd qu\u00e1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t&rdquo; &ndash; Alan Shearer nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Top 4 Premier League 2018/19.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</span></span></div>\r\n<table class=\"MsoTableGrid\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"width:100.0%;background:#FFFFCC;border-collapse:collapse;border:none;&#10; mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-yfti-tbllook:1184;mso-padding-alt:&#10; 0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:0;mso-yfti-firstrow:yes;mso-yfti-lastrow:yes\">\r\n            <td width=\"100%\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:100.0%;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;&#10;  mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt\">\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;  justify;line-height:normal\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n c\u1ee7a   Shearer v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua m\u00f9a n\u00e0y</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">1. Man City</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">2. Liverpool</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">3. Man United</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">4. Tottenham</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">5. Chelsea</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">6. Arsenal</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/shearer-dung-voi-gach-ten-mu-khoi-danh-sach-ung-vien-vo-dich-172-194084.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/shearer-dung-voi-gach-ten-mu-khoi-danh-sach-ung-vien-vo-dich.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/shearer-dung-voi-gach-ten-mu-khoi-danh-sach-ung-vien-vo-dich-172-194084.html\">Shearer: S\u1ebd l\u00e0 ngu ng\u1ed1c n\u1ebfu g\u1ea1ch t\u00ean M.U kh\u1ecfi cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch</span><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y tr\u00ean BBC, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Alan Shearer cho r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u1ea1t t\u00ean M.U kh\u1ecfi cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 h\u1ecd v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pep-guardiola-man-city-se-con-khung-khiep-hon-nua-172-194039.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/pep-guardiola-man-city-se-con-khung-khiep-hon-nua.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pep-guardiola-man-city-se-con-khung-khiep-hon-nua-172-194039.html\">Pep Guardiola: Man City s\u1ebd c\u00f2n kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp h\u01a1n n\u1eefa</span><br>\r\nSau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i si\u00eau c\u00fap n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, HLV Pep Guardiola kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City c\u00f2n m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n n\u1eefa so v\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nNguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5275","checkdouble":"194088"},{"date":"10:55 09/08","title":"Wayne Rooney: \"MU ch\u1ec9 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19 n\u1ebfu...\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/7/9/wayne-rooney-mu-chi-vo-dich-ngoai-hang-anh-201819-neu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Wayne Rooney ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a t\u1edbi n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Rooney mu\u1ed1n MU mua th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, M.U m\u1edbi chi 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 3 t\u00e2n binh, trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 duy nh\u1ea5t Fred \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d. HLV Mourinho kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh mua s\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Man \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rooney muon la dien vien chinh\" title=\"Rooney mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0 di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean ch\u00ednh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2013/10/rooneyichky3-20131010212615.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Rooney mu\u1ed1n MU mua th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua s\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, nh\u01b0ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u00f4ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng 50% y\u00eau c\u1ea7u. V\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 55 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf chi th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nWayne Rooney ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a t\u1edbi n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng M.U s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi, t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd mang v\u1ec1 th\u00eam 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn. Khi m\u00e0 Man City r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh c\u00f2n Liverpool \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, n\u1ebfu M.U kh\u00f4ng b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, t\u00f4i tin t\u01b0\u1edfng BL\u0110 s\u1ebd mang v\u1ec1 cho Mourinho th\u00eam nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh. Mourinho \u0111ang kh\u00e1t khao nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng \u1ea5y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u00e0 th\u00f4i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M.U quan t\u00e2m r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ecdi n\u0103m, nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a M.U xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u00e0n ng\u1eadp tr\u00ean kh\u1eafp c\u00e1c m\u1eb7t b\u00e1o. H\u00f4m nay l\u00e0 ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mua th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, NHM Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1edbi Old Trafford.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Wayne Rooney ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Wayne Rooney ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/27/Wayne-Rooney-phat-bieu-ve-MU-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Harry Maguire v\u00e0 Toby Alderweireld l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam trung v\u1ec7. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/tottenham-cho-mu-them-mot-co-hoi-chieu-mo-alderweireld-172-194081.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU quan t\u00e2m Toby Alderweireld </span>c\u1ee7a Tottenham, ngo\u00e0i ra nh\u1eefng Harry Maguire (Leicester), Boateng (Bayern Munich) v\u00e0 Zouma (Chelsea) c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 nh\u1eafm Sergej Milinkovic-Savic c\u1ee7a Lazio, Toni Kroos c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, Verratti c\u1ee7a PSG hay Ramsey c\u1ee7a Arsenal.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a M.U, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i Danny Rose c\u1ee7a Tottenham, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Willian c\u1ee7a Chelsea hay c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Ivan Perisic c\u1ee7a Inter Milan.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5274","checkdouble":"194089"},{"date":"11:33 09/08","title":"MU ch\u1ed1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Paul Pogba","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/mu-chot-tuong-lai-paul-pogba.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Paul Pogba r\u1eddi MU \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao, theo Express Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ra \u0111i \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca quan t\u00e2m Pogba</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 Anh \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0a tin <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/tin-chuyen-nhuong/nong-paul-pogba-dat-thoa-thuan-voi-barca-187-193906.html\" target=\"_blank\">Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Paul Pogba</span> c\u1ee7a M.U. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111ang c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Iniesta \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng Paul Pogba r\u1eddi MU \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mourinho ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng Paul Pogba r\u1eddi MU \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/Mourinho-chan-duong-Paul-Pogba-roi-MU-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Pogba</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Ernesto Valverde \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Pogba v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n BL\u0110 Barca \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993.\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Pogba, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t cao, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o cho anh m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. Bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c M.U kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 130 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1edd The Sun v\u00e0 Mirror kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Pogba mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi M.U \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Barca, anh mu\u1ed1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a m\u00ecnh c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Camp Nou \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M.U tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Pogba</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Paul Pogba r\u1eddi MU \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao, theo Express Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ra \u0111i \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho phat bieu ve Pogba\" title=\"Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Pogba\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/mu-chot-tuong-lai-paul-pogba.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef Pogba \u1edf l\u1ea1i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMourinho tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 Pogba kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e1n, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 coi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, b\u1edfi v\u1eady d\u00f9 c\u00f3 chi nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2u Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Pogba.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM.U \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn Mourinho h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng, theo \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 chi 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 3 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. Khi m\u00e0 qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi \u0111ang g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n th\u00ec Man \u0111\u1ecf \u01b0u ti\u00ean gi\u1eef nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Pogba, M.U c\u0169ng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Lukaku, Martial hay Bailly. Song song v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford c\u0169ng t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5273","checkdouble":"194090"},{"date":"11:12 09/08","title":"Chelsea l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1edbi Kepa: \u201cChim s\u1ebb\u201d c\u00f3 h\u00f3t vang t\u1ea1i London?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/chelsea-chieu-mo-kepa-arrizabalaga-chim-se-co-hot-vang-tai-london.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Kepa Arrizabalaga th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb Athletic Bilbao. Ch\u1ec9 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i cho \u0111\u1ed9i 1 v\u1edbi 54 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 24 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn The Blues ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u00ean t\u1edbi 80 tri\u1ec7u Euro (72 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng) \u0111\u1ec3 mang anh v\u1ec1 th\u00e0nh London.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kepa t\u1edbi Chelsea thay Courtois</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;<em>T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Kepa thi \u0111\u1ea5u 1 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc. \u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i v\u1ec1 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y n\u1eb1m \u1edf t\u00e0i n\u0103ng xu\u1ea5t ch\u00fang. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t tr\u1ebb song b\u1eaft r\u1ea5t hay</em>&rdquo;, HLV Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Kepa Arrizabalaga th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb Athletic Bilbao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1o c\u00e1o t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u1eeb c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n tr\u1ea1ch vi\u00ean Chelsea t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1ec1 Kepa, Sarri th\u00eam ph\u1ea7n h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, The Blues r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi. Nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Thibaut Courtois \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfn tri\u1ec3n g\u00ec su\u1ed1t v\u00e0i th\u00e1ng qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Kepa Arrizabalaga th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb Athletic Bilbao h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Kepa Arrizabalaga th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb Athletic Bilbao h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/Chelsea-chieu-mo-Kepa-Arrizabalaga-thanh-cong-tu-Athletic-Bilbao-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Courtois \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ecfa gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 t\u1edbi Real</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00e3i ng\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn. Trong khi Courtois mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eadn 300 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng/ tu\u1ea7n m\u1edbi ch\u1ecbu \u1edf l\u1ea1i th\u00ec Chelsea ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e0 n\u1eeda ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u00f3. Ngay sau khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb World Cup 2018, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ec9 th\u00f4ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ee9c h\u00fat c\u1ee7a Real Madrid v\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u00e0 m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng h\u1ecd d\u00e0nh cho tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ch\u1ea5t x\u00fac t\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1i t\u1eeb v\u1edbi Courtois. \u0110\u00e3 h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n ngh\u1ec9 ph\u00e9p, anh v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. B\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n g\u1eb7p m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c, Courtois m\u1ed9t m\u1ef1c l\u00e1nh m\u1eb7t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-chinh-thuc-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-thu-mon-courtois-180-194067.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/real-madrid-chinh-thuc-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-thu-mon-courtois.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-chinh-thuc-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-thu-mon-courtois-180-194067.html\">Real Madrid CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Courtois</span><br>\r\n<span>Real Madrid v\u1eeba ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 vi\u1ec7c mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Thibaut Courtois t\u1eeb Chelsea v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Los...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t h\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea5t y\u1ebfu, Chelsea bu\u1ed9c l\u00f2ng ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n kh\u00e1c thay th\u1ebf. Sau khi c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau, The Blues ch\u1ed1t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n Kepa Arrizabalaga. Ph\u00eda Bilbao th\u00ec d\u1ee9t kho\u00e1t kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu nh\u1ea3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi h\u1ecd h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2018 v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do Chelsea bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea1nh b\u1ea1o k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 80 tri\u1ec7u Euro (72 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng) v\u1edbi Kepa. Sau khi gi\u1ea3i ng\u00e2n s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ebfch x\u00f9 n\u00e0y, th\u00f4ng qua \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n sinh n\u0103m 1994 v\u00e0 n\u1ed9p l\u00ean tr\u1ee5 s\u1edf c\u1ee7a La Liga, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1edbi Kepa Chim s\u1ebb c\u00f3 h\u00f3t vang t\u1ea1i London h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Chelsea l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1edbi Kepa Chim s\u1ebb c\u00f3 h\u00f3t vang t\u1ea1i London h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/chelsea-chieu-mo-kepa-arrizabalaga-chim-se-co-hot-vang-tai-london.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Kepa Arrizabalaga t\u1eeb Athletic Bilbao</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tu\u1ed5i s\u1eafp 24, Kepa Arrizabalaga \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. M\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u Euro c\u1ee7a anh v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua con s\u1ed1 63 tri\u1ec7u Euro m\u00e0 Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf ra \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Alisson t\u1eeb Roma c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 3 tu\u1ea7n. \u0110\u00e1ng n\u00f3i \u1edf ch\u1ed7, Kepa \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi khi m\u1edbi b\u1eaft 54 tr\u1eadn cho \u0111\u1ed9i 1 Bilbao tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, th\u1ea7y c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Kepa \u1edf Real Valladolid m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2015/16 (cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1eeb Bilbao) l\u00e0 Miguel \u00c1ngel Portugal l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. &ldquo;<em>Ngo\u00e0i s\u1ef1 nhanh nh\u1eb9n, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, Kepa c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1eabu th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n r\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng gian c\u1ea3 trong v\u00e0 ngo\u00e0i v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m. Phong c\u00e1ch \u01b0a th\u00edch l\u00e0m b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 r\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi HLV Sarri</em>&rdquo;, Portugal chia s\u1ebb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Kepa\" title=\"thu mon Kepa\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/Kepa-Arrizabalaga-o-dau-khi-so-sanh-voi-Courtois-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Kepa \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2018, Kepa \u0111\u00e3 su\u00fdt l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. Tuy nhi\u00ean, d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng 20 tri\u1ec7u Euro c\u00f9ng Bilbao v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00ean l\u1ecbch ra m\u1eaft, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Florentino P\u00e9rez c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c c\u1ed9ng s\u1ef1 v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i h\u1ee7y th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u00fd do l\u00e0 b\u1edfi HLV c\u1ee7a Real khi \u0111\u00f3: Zinedine Zidane d\u1ee9t kho\u00e1t kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd. Trong \u0111\u1ed9i 1 Los Blancos l\u00fac \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n bao g\u1ed3m Keylor Navas, Kiko Casilla v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Luca Zidane, con trai Zizou. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Real ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft trong vi\u1ec7c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Kepa, song h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn nghe theo \u00fd ki\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f2n Kepa, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1edd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Bilbao k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn h\u01a1n. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c, ch\u00e0ng trai 24 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi CLB \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o ra m\u00ecnh. V\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd, Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Kepa Arrizabalaga th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u Euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kepa va Courtois\" title=\"Kepa va Courtois\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/Kepa-va-Courtois.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Kepa c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 thay th\u1ebf Courtois t\u1ea1i Chelsea</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>&ldquo;Chim s\u1ebb&rdquo; c\u00f3 h\u00f3t vang?</h2>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Kepa c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7t danh El Jilguero (Chim s\u1ebb c\u00e1nh v\u00e0ng). Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng pha bay l\u01b0\u1ee3n nh\u01b0 chim, anh th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 y\u00eau th\u00edch lo\u00e0i v\u1eadt n\u00e0y. Ni\u1ec1m \u0111am m\u00ea ch\u01a1i chim c\u1ee7a anh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb khi c\u00f2n nh\u1ecf, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1eeba h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi cha.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00e0y Kepa ra m\u1eaft Chelsea, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta l\u1ea1i v\u00ed anh nh\u01b0 ch\u00fa chim s\u1ebb \u0111i v\u00e0o v\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ea5t n\u1eafng m\u01b0a th\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng London. Su\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m qua, Chelsea r\u01a1i v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng b\u1ea5t \u1ed5n. C\u1ee9 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, ngay sau \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i l\u00e2m v\u00e0o kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn r\u1ed3i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ch\u00f3ng v\u00e1nh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kepa thich choi chim tu nho\" title=\"Kepa thich choi chim tu nho\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/Kepa-thich-choi-chim-tu-nho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Kepa th\u00edch ch\u01a1i chim t\u1eeb thu\u1edf nh\u1ecf</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nRi\u00eang v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n, s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Kepa \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1edbn trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea. HLV Sarri d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh tri\u1ec3n khai l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p ng\u1eafn, ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng ngay t\u1eeb ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1o t\u1ea1i The Blues. C\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Pep Guardiola t\u1ea1i Man City, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0o c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i theo phong c\u00e1ch nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t d\u1eabn t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Chelsea ch\u1ecdn Kepa thay v\u00ec ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m h\u01a1n nh\u01b0 Jack Butland c\u1ee7a Stoke City. Vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd tr\u1ea3 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u0169ng c\u00f3 c\u00e1i l\u00fd c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Song ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u \u00e1p l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Kepa t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 nh\u1ecf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kepa Arrizabalaga bat chac tay truoc Real\" title=\"Kepa Arrizabalaga bat chac tay truoc Real\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/19/Kepa-Arrizabalaga-bat-chac-tay-truoc-Real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00c1p l\u1ef1c d\u00e0nh cho ch\u00e0ng trai 24 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh g\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng ng\u00e0n c\u00e2n \u0111\u00e8 l\u00ean vai, m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh c\u0169ng h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n r\u1ea5t kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t cho Kepa. \u0110\u1ebfn David De Gea trong 1, 2 m\u00f9a \u0111\u1ea7u khi t\u1edbi Man United c\u0169ng m\u1eafc ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m ng\u1edb ng\u1ea9n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng sau \u0111\u00f3, De Gea \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1ng tin c\u1eady c\u1ee7a M.U. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Chelsea c\u0169ng hy v\u1ecdng Kepa s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u01a1n t\u1edbi t\u1ea7m v\u00f3c \u0111\u00f3, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n nhanh h\u01a1n \u0111\u00e0n anh. Th\u1ea7y c\u0169 Portugal \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o El Jilguero s\u1ebd l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y: &ldquo;<em>Kepa c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 th\u1eed th\u00e1ch n\u00e0o</em>&rdquo;, \u00f4ng k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/day-top-10-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-184-194091.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/day-top-10-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/day-top-10-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-184-194091.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Top 10 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</span><br>\r\n<span>V\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 bom t\u1ea5n 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Kepa c\u1ee7a Chelsea v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Alisson \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u Top 10 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>C\u00f9ng chi\u00eam ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kepa Arrizabalaga:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/9/Kepa-Arrizabalaga.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Chelsea tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-chelsea-truoc-mua-giai-201819-tan-cong-va-hon-the-nua-172-193858.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19: T\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 h\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u1eefa</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-sieu-cup-anh-2018-thanh-bai-cua-sarri-va-bai-hoc-man-city-cho-chelsea-172-193820.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Si\u00eau C\u00fap Anh 2018: Th\u00e0nh b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Sarri v\u00e0 b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc Man City cho Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/diem-nhan-tran-chelsea-vs-man-city-sieu-cup-anh-2018-172-193809.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n r\u00fat ra t\u1eeb tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap Anh 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-02-man-city-co-mot-napoli-phien-ban-loi-xuat-hien-172-193804.html\">Chelsea 0-2 Man City: C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t Napoli phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n l\u1ed7i xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5272","checkdouble":"194094"},{"date":"11:59 09/08","title":"Gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 Kepa Arrizabalaga \u2013 T\u00e2n binh 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/9/giai-ma-kepa-arrizabalaga-tan-binh-71-trieu-bang-cua-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u00edch n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n. V\u1eady Kepa Arrizabalaga l\u00e0 ai?\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kepa v\u00e0 h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh t\u1edbi Chelsea</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 David De Gea kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 s\u1edf, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha Real Madrid chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau Kepa Arrizabalaga c\u1ee7a Athletic Bilbao, v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1&hellip; 20 tri\u1ec7u euro. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i, HLV Zidane \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi \u0111\u00f3, Real Madrid ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Keylor Navas. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Zidane d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y m\u1eb7n m\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n, nh\u1eb1m d\u1ecdn ch\u1ed7 cho con trai m\u00ecnh (Luca Zidane \u0111ang l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Real Madrid). Sau c\u00f9ng, Kepa \u0111\u00e3 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Bilbao c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kepa Arrizabalaga l\u00e0 ai Gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 t\u00e2n binh 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 1\" title=\"Kepa Arrizabalaga l\u00e0 ai Gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 t\u00e2n binh 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/Kepa-Arrizabalaga-la-ai-Giai-ma-tan-binh-71-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kepa ch\u00fat n\u1eefa tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Navas \u1edf Real</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m nay, K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Thibaut Courtois v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u euro (do anh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng). Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Chelsea loay hoay v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c nhau, r\u1ed3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh &ldquo;b\u1ed1c&rdquo; Kepa b\u1eb1ng gi\u00e1 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng (v\u00ec Bilbao kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n), qua \u0111\u00f3 bi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 v\u1eeba qua, Kepa c\u0169ng g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1edbi vai tr\u00f2 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a B\u00f2 t\u00f3t l\u00e0 David De Gea, ti\u1ebfp theo l\u00e0 Pepe Reina v\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng l\u00e0 Kepa &ndash; t\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge. Sau khi gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t bi\u1ebft \u01a1n CLB v\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kepa Arrizabalaga l\u00e0 ai Gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 t\u00e2n binh 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Kepa va Courtois\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/Kepa-va-Courtois.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1edbi Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 Courtois</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>Phong c\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 r\u1ea5t nhanh, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng di chuy\u1ec3n, ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Kepa c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. N\u00f3i c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c, anh ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u1edbi h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng m\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111ang x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi t\u00e2n HLV Sarri, m\u1ed9t m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tri\u1ec3n khai b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 (c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1eabu th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u01b0a th\u00edch c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh U19 T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u n\u0103m 2012, Kepa \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 2 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n trong tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p. Cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m 2017, anh m\u1edbi l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra m\u1eaft \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 5-0 c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha tr\u01b0\u1edbc Costa Rica.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sinh ng\u00e0y 3/10/1994, Kepa v\u1eabn c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t tr\u1ebb so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Bilbao \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 54 tr\u1eadn. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong m\u1ecdi c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n tham d\u1ef1 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng v\u1eeba qua sau khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n sang Real Madrid, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u00eam 7 n\u0103m c\u00f9ng Atletic Bilbao (\u0111\u1ebfn 2025). Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y, Kepa t\u1eebng n\u00f3i: &ldquo;T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf l\u1ea1i ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 15 n\u0103m t\u1eeb khi 9 tu\u1ed5i, v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Bilbao. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 C\u0110V nhi\u1ec7t th\u00e0nh nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kepa Arrizabalaga l\u00e0 ai Gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 t\u00e2n binh 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Kepa Arrizabalaga\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/15/o-lai-man-utd-de-gea-tien-cu-dan-em-cho-real-madrid.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kepa l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh r\u1ea5t ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Bilbao</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1eaft, nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kepa Arrizabalaga ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t gi\u00e0u ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng, nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a anh v\u00e0i th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 20 tri\u1ec7u euro. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u1eabn c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi l\u1edbn. N\u1ebfu so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi bom t\u1ea5n Alisson m\u00e0 Liverpool v\u1eeba k\u00edch n\u1ed5, Kepa \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng kh\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng, nh\u01b0ng m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1eaft h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, Chelsea bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u1eafn r\u0103ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 T\u00e2y Ban Nha, b\u1edfi vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Willy Caballero b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh h\u1ebft tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y qua tr\u1eadn kh\u00e1c, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng hay cho l\u1eafm. T\u00e2n binh Robert Green, t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng \u0111em l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 m\u1ea5y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kepa Arrizabalaga l\u00e0 ai Gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 t\u00e2n binh 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" title=\"Kepa l\u00e0 ai\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/kepa.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Chelsea \u0111ang \u0111\u1eb7t c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kepa Arrizabalaga l\u00e0 ai?</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nR\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, vi\u1ec7c bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u1edbi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro cho m\u1ed9t t\u00e0i n\u0103ng ch\u01b0a ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u &ndash; BL\u0110 Chelsea \u0111ang b\u1ecb c\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u1ea1o. V\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 n\u00e0y (th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u00edt h\u01a1n), h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ngay t\u1eeb Premier League, v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o l\u1edbn h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi ngay c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c C\u0110V c\u1ee7a Chelsea, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn ng\u01a1 ng\u00e1c v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi Kepa Arrizabalaga l\u00e0 ai. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9, v\u00e0 ngay c\u1ea3 HLV Maurizio Sarri l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng Kepa x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u1ecf ra. M\u1ed9t David De Gea m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-chieu-mo-kepa-arrizabalaga-chim-se-co-hot-vang-tai-london-172-194094.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/chelsea-chieu-mo-kepa-arrizabalaga-chim-se-co-hot-vang-tai-london.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-chieu-mo-kepa-arrizabalaga-chim-se-co-hot-vang-tai-london-172-194094.html\">Chelsea l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1edbi Kepa: &ldquo;Chim s\u1ebb&rdquo; c\u00f3 h\u00f3t vang t\u1ea1i London?</span><br>\r\nChelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Kepa Arrizabalaga th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb Athletic Bilbao. Ch\u1ec9 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i cho \u0111\u1ed9i 1 v\u1edbi 54 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 24 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn The...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/day-top-10-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-184-194091.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/day-top-10-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/day-top-10-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-184-194091.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Top 10 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 bom t\u1ea5n 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Kepa c\u1ee7a Chelsea v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Alisson \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u Top 10 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5271","checkdouble":"194099"}]}